the operative word here being *unreviewed*. The phrase

> "I asked ChatGPT and this is what it said: <...>".

Is a generic disclosure. It can just as easily mean

> "Your question stimulated my curiosity and here's the synthesis of what I've learned after going back and forth with an LLM for 20min:"
